  "texts": [
    "As a result, carrying out a critical examination of replies and considering steps to eliminate any biases is vital for ensuring fair and unbiased teaching.",
    "Inconsistent outputsGenerative AI can produce different responses to the same prompt, which can be problematic in an educational setting [140].",
    "For instance, it may provide contradictory responses on the same topic, causing confusion.",
    "Second, it can produce responses of varying quality [60].",
    "For instance, in a recent study, 3 researchers at the exact same location asked the exact same question simultaneously to an LLM-chatbot, yet they obtained three different responses of varying quality [147]."
